<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>NatWest's online services have gone down across the UK with many customers being left locked out of their accounts. </p>

<p>Many have been complaining on social media of their money disappearing, being unable to make payments or even log in.</p>

<p>A spokesperson said: 'We've been made aware of this issue and we're investigating it now as a matter of urgency. </p>

<p>NatWest's online services have gone down across the UK with many customers being left locked out of their accounts</p>

<p>'We hope to have this resolved as soon as possible. </p>

<p>'We sincerely appreciate your patience at this time and wholeheartedly apologise for any inconvenience.'</p>
